function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	-- Vigo spots and runs to wounded knight
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVigoAtHoist, locVigoAtWoundedKnight, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVigoAtHoist, locVigoAtWoundedKnight)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorVigoAtHoist, animsetVigoKneel)
	
	-- Ney walks toward wounded knight
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, 1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, locNeyrelleAtWoundedKnight, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, locNeyrelleAtWoundedKnight)
end

end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convNeyrellePetals, idActor)

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
		
	--Neyrelle follower becomes static
	followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_NEYRELLE_FOLLOWER)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.QActorEnableAI(followerNeyrelle, false);
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerNeyrelle);
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerNeyrelle, locNeyAtPetals, "NPC_Run", true);
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerNeyrelle, locNeyAtPetals);
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerNeyrelle) then
		Hydra.ActorDisable(followerNeyrelle)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(followerNeyrelle)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(actorNeyAtPetals)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorNeyrelleAtHoist)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	-- This delay allows the door to play its entire animation before being phased out
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--Cleanup Neyrelle from phases 4-5
	Hydra.ActorDisable(actorNeyAtPetals)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(actorNeyAtPetals)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	-- Player Announced They Found the Entrance
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convDGNEntranceFound, idActor)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Neyrelle move action
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, false)
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, 0.15)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, locNeyrelleGate, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorNeyrelleAtHoist, locNeyrelleGate)
	
	-- Vigo move action
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(actorVigoAtHoist, false)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorVigoAtHoist, locVigoGate, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorVigoAtHoist, locVigoGate)
end
